::DarkMouse::

She tried to mover her head and does so.  She moves it against the 
hand on her head.  She opens her eyes and sees BlackAracnia.  She 
whispers,"thank you."  Then closes her eyes again.  Even doing that 
much was a strain.  Se rested and hoped she would be able to fight 
agaain. Someday.
